{"type": "article", "id": 12444, "title": "隐身凳子", "description": "", "date": "2015-07-22T07:45:23Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 20, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606000223DIS0w9Jl2KVYerWd.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t设计师 Jinsik Kim 用石头和金属材料一起做了一个凳子，重量较轻的金属桌凳面被安置在一个 “U” 形的石头支架上面，金属面会反射石头的纹理以及周边环境的模样，看起来就像是一个隐身的凳子，虽然搬运问题看起来不太好解决，但相信坐在上面拍照应该会很好玩。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140157k1mBvETnPXycoWhz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140157CugqWVNFJlwZH2he.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140158M4AODodNeZU790K3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.69333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140158CSk3bWmU7p12qXvE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140159koP8mvaCQVFI4eLr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}